{"tid":796184,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩今次港股同我夾夾夾,夾死班淡友,往死裡夾","createTime":"2018-08-27T14:43:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T04:51:51.000Z","uid":79081,"like":41,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"1176bbfe5314d830c2363ac4c81c8393f72f1d92","tid":796184,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"利益伸報左先,年頭一路觀望,唔敢亦都無自信入市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最終摸左頂,3萬2入左市,執少少唔肯走,之後跌落三萬忍痛止蝕清晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港股徘徊3萬點果排,各位有印象都記得穿完3萬就即刻升返,曾經有一段上落市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n卒之最後跌落2萬9,我忍唔住又出左手,仲要大手買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後結果大家心裡有數,寫十個慘字都唔夠,恆生指數一直跌,更可怕的係各種大股好似黑色暴雨咁一直落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無錯, 騰訊 ,舜宇, 建設銀行 仲有各種藍籌,呢段期間帳面無左6位數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我明白6位數字對各位黎講只係散紙,但呢D錢,係我靠打工,死慳死抵,一蚊一毫咁儲返黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛市熊市係一個經濟循環,願賭亦都要服輸,本來只打算執少少食餐豪,估唔到嬴粒糖輸間廠<br />\n<br />\n個感覺就係心如止水,諗住繼續自己前途黑暗既人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而,呢段期間,每日上親財經台,圍爐取暖既人當然有<br />\n<br />\n但更加多既係 一班一朝得志既淡友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自問平生無做咩虧心事,玩都只係玩正股,大藍籌<br />\n<br />\n呢班淡友,講既野真係惡毒到不堪入目,恥笑緊同我一樣坐緊貨既苦主都算<br />\n<br />\n有班人仲每日開PO,用自己既燈力,想燈港股繼續向下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢班人, 差唔多每日都要開一個PO,講話聽日會升幾多點,聽日會係大奇跡日,明捧暗踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地呢班苦主,每日睇住呢D PO, 真係心都UP埋 , 終於明白咩叫攞景又贈興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢段時間既財經台,比呢D 一D質素都無既PO 佔晒位,洗晒版<br />\n<br />\n我實在唔明呢D人係咩心態<br />\n<br />\n股市原質上只有望佢升先會有錢賺,有班人唔望升,反望跌,有正股唔玩,係都要玩衍生工具<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句,你地同民國時期,日本侵華既漢奸,有咩分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地既分別就係,漢奸叛國理直氣壯,佢地有自己既理由,原因<br />\n<br />\n當中可能會有落井下石之輩,亦有身在曹營身在漢之人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但呢班仆街死淡友....清一色落井下石...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n落井下石之餘,仲要同班受苦受難既香港人講,加油啊,聽日有人拯救你地啊,你地撐住啊....<br />\n<br />\n我真係R爆頭都諗唔明,點解會有咁多將自己快樂建築係別人痛苦身上既人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望今次港股可以生生性性,一路爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夾死班淡友,夾到佢地灰飛煙滅,往死裡夾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b4266ba143557c627c083c36d8883b9f5a9416","tid":796184,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8f115feb0f36702965f4866e2f9ea08edd18c4","tid":796184,"uid":190540,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:46:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55cf2b9e86447f36014b75bbe9518c443e8c3fe1","tid":796184,"uid":48767,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:48:42.000Z","msg":"又一個輸到傻左"},{"pid":"932782ba8d6ad4d3fe21d2ad8c5739464e6575c7","tid":796184,"uid":48294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:49:11.000Z","msg":"你好似鬧埋自己wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601dac6078e63fc8a224cb44c5afae9715b594a0","tid":796184,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"玩熊市點可以唔聽沈大師?"},{"pid":"bf63c668c99c556b06489d9400e24ec446a732e2","tid":796184,"uid":163916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:53:54.000Z","msg":"害你輸嘅人係托高個市散貨嘅大戶，唔係淡友。"},{"pid":"28399ad058843536b1653d0b66e8e43a570362fe","tid":796184,"uid":141263,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"怪自己爛賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你本質上同班熊證淡友一樣 都係賭仔。唔好呃自己買大藍鬼係正氣 其實本質都冇分別 琴日你輸 今佢地輸 都係輸係個「貪」字上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f382ce9764859ddde9c4d69d34c7091dd9dc2fb4","tid":796184,"uid":141263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28399ad058843536b1653d0b66e8e43a570362fe","tid":796184,"uid":141263,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"怪自己爛賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你本質上同班熊證淡友一樣 都係賭仔。唔好呃自己買大藍鬼係正氣 其實本質都冇分別 琴日你輸 今佢地輸 都係輸係個「貪」字上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"*大藍籌"},{"pid":"23f4f3093680600fd3556ed7608529f4c15c14be","tid":796184,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:04:02.000Z","msg":"唔明點解你要屌衍生工具，<br />\n你用兩萬炒牛證等於廿幾三十萬正股。<br />\n如果你炒衍生衰極都係兩萬，今日損失就細好多。"},{"pid":"247c7b629eb47ad25995dc090f94bdc0a75ddb9f","tid":796184,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:05:42.000Z","msg":"買股票輸錢潮文？"},{"pid":"57a1dbbfd260f246be9a77914cd40e15be7402e7","tid":796184,"uid":28355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:11:09.000Z","msg":"今日真係往死裡夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568d90d3d545a406797faba96bb84a0062e1651c","tid":796184,"uid":25641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:16:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"321ac43883e35d755a27cd8aa9ed818039d00bd5","tid":796184,"uid":49102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"3萬2買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbc14691320162fe25350d8ba23599c26f7d2ab","tid":796184,"uid":33338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:18:56.000Z","msg":"放心 期結完又會趺返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8137e696b55df548096f6a9f21881656eada421","tid":796184,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"正股 驚西咩？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留比個孫做古董啦"},{"pid":"c79f02d831d163bb6aa6053fe95f455b3d177a30","tid":796184,"uid":101485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:21:23.000Z","msg":"沽既本質係比你對沖 你唔沽埋一份輸錢關人咩事<br />\n人地沽空 咁升個陣一樣收皮 <br />\n大把人沽空夾到破產無出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc1a4721789a1c1dff4966bec685ccd069e7620","tid":796184,"uid":77905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:21:36.000Z","msg":"用感情嚟炒股？"},{"pid":"780720ef5ac6b8ed0125bf0b3b5c2d1cacb46d50","tid":796184,"uid":77186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:23:21.000Z","msg":"夾死班淡友"},{"pid":"4dccaa50dec72f1eef7d9314b728cbd46294efab","tid":796184,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:34:46.000Z","msg":"潮文？"},{"pid":"4488698928ca4a04ac7b67233f4e2266bc0c4381","tid":796184,"uid":24721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"你咁樣玩藍籌我比一億你都輸曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a106f14aa5c8e76adabcaa97ced0a7e58e8acd58","tid":796184,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:44:32.000Z","msg":"自己唔對沖唔比人對沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ab2280a035dbe6cb5a7105f3c8a078b990048f","tid":796184,"uid":201960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"股票市場即係一個賭場, 有人睇好, 有人睇淡, 睇好既人, 會坐埋去睇好既賭枱, and vice versa<br />\n唔同人有唔同玩法, 唔好怪人地唔同你坐埋同一張枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21b80478b134592b3cc27b538daaf537d427b5a","tid":796184,"uid":94836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:10:11.000Z","msg":"樓市介唔介意講下買左乜?<br />\n睇你個樣好似all in 晒一d科技銀行ed上落幅度大既股。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c6c19d40c215442d1f6cc740b6d5b9fc3baed5","tid":796184,"uid":180523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:26:59.000Z","msg":"睇黎Ching真係輸好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abf6e5c19c9d22533367b6e6caae081a0c5cb41","tid":796184,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1176bbfe5314d830c2363ac4c81c8393f72f1d92","tid":796184,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"利益伸報左先,年頭一路觀望,唔敢亦都無自信入市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最終摸左頂,3萬2入左市,執少少唔肯走,之後跌落三萬忍痛止蝕清晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港股徘徊3萬點果排,各位有印象都記得穿完3萬就即刻升返,曾經有一段上落市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n卒之最後跌落2萬9,我忍唔住又出左手,仲要大手買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後結果大家心裡有數,寫十個慘字都唔夠,恆生指數一直跌,更可怕的係各種大股好似黑色暴雨咁一直落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無錯, 騰訊 ,舜宇, 建設銀行 仲有各種藍籌,呢段期間帳面無左6位數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我明白6位數字對各位黎講只係散紙,但呢D錢,係我靠打工,死慳死抵,一蚊一毫咁儲返黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛市熊市係一個經濟循環,願賭亦都要服輸,本來只打算執少少食餐豪,估唔到嬴粒糖輸間廠<br />\n<br />\n個感覺就係心如止水,諗住繼續自己前途黑暗既人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而,呢段期間,每日上親財經台,圍爐取暖既人當然有<br />\n<br />\n但更加多既係 一班一朝得志既淡友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自問平生無做咩虧心事,玩都只係玩正股,大藍籌<br />\n<br />\n呢班淡友,講既野真係惡毒到不堪入目,恥笑緊同我一樣坐緊貨既苦主都算<br />\n<br />\n有班人仲每日開PO,用自己既燈力,想燈港股繼續向下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢班人, 差唔多每日都要開一個PO,講話聽日會升幾多點,聽日會係大奇跡日,明捧暗踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地呢班苦主,每日睇住呢D PO, 真係心都UP埋 , 終於明白咩叫攞景又贈興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢段時間既財經台,比呢D 一D質素都無既PO 佔晒位,洗晒版<br />\n<br />\n我實在唔明呢D人係咩心態<br />\n<br />\n股市原質上只有望佢升先會有錢賺,有班人唔望升,反望跌,有正股唔玩,係都要玩衍生工具<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句,你地同民國時期,日本侵華既漢奸,有咩分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地既分別就係,漢奸叛國理直氣壯,佢地有自己既理由,原因<br />\n<br />\n當中可能會有落井下石之輩,亦有身在曹營身在漢之人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但呢班仆街死淡友....清一色落井下石...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n落井下石之餘,仲要同班受苦受難既香港人講,加油啊,聽日有人拯救你地啊,你地撐住啊....<br />\n<br />\n我真係R爆頭都諗唔明,點解會有咁多將自己快樂建築係別人痛苦身上既人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望今次港股可以生生性性,一路爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夾死班淡友,夾到佢地灰飛煙滅,往死裡夾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:31:54.000Z","msg":"正put 驚西"},{"pid":"5f81abb294edfc828677f96a6d9d6dff26836fd8","tid":796184,"uid":36519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:37:28.000Z","msg":"自己冇眼光關人咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cffefd41bb00b07a04cd375bc11d72fdc197c6","tid":796184,"uid":62443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"3萬2入市<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443e1ebb53596d28e9f307445b0becdeb6ddfdc1","tid":796184,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:24:15.000Z","msg":"支持夾死淡友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3b82b3ef30397230022a82e3763074976e0b5c","tid":796184,"uid":103802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:27:02.000Z","msg":"挾死左佢地 咪無人托住個市<br />\n我仲想玩耐d <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4445dbeb688060142bbe863f320c2a5437783560","tid":796184,"uid":64733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:33:32.000Z","msg":"呢篇係潮文黎？"},{"pid":"f9ae2a9c35ad70b7302d06d5f7edf325bcabd1dc","tid":796184,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:40:36.000Z","msg":"長揸驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcc8114f3bcade3f8c0b424de927be85bd40d8f","tid":796184,"uid":153102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T19:43:13.000Z","msg":"你渣大藍籌唔明點解要放,我睇你輸得6位數字你投資金額都應該夠1球<br />\n<br />\n每年坐定定收息其實冇問題"},{"pid":"7ca11eeeff55967881548f537be0951ccef0bd1d","tid":796184,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T00:00:07.000Z","msg":"用自己既燈力令港股繼續向下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c02a2063b3107e22356f6a1dc3595f2c53c0b4","tid":796184,"uid":37599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T00:09:30.000Z","msg":"勢色唔對就唔好上黎是常識吧<br />\n你而家出個咁既post,  一跌就俾人推返上黎bin屍，何苦呢&hellip;"},{"pid":"3c76bc16d4611e6901fc20dfe16f606a7efd878a","tid":796184,"uid