"uid":187956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:52:00.000Z","msg":"好撚痛呀係咁夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53effdde517c3c705928d97eea8973c84b71f0d3","tid":796184,"uid":116718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aacaa808dbda0e1c26de5cfe660f06ce64910c0","tid":796184,"uid":129741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:01:33.000Z","msg":"痛"},{"pid":"5643a6193cb7c63b5616d0cd922cf41f9c067fc0","tid":796184,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a40e58bdcb42ea4edd71dd1518d07e338587987","tid":796184,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:44:10.000Z","msg":"DKLM,今次又中伏,跌撚返晒<br />\n唔玩啦,比返D錢我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eda918fa8f1ce770349906af5972265fc990461","tid":796184,"uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a40e58bdcb42ea4edd71dd1518d07e338587987","tid":796184,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:44:10.000Z","msg":"DKLM,今次又中伏,跌撚返晒<br />\n唔玩啦,比返D錢我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T09:11:21.000Z","msg":"止蝕啦，股災啦"},{"pid":"5e2e05b4e92ddbb7c4c18394f6a8cd1dbbf00a93","tid":796184,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T09:14:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cd2e4801ad0f51f292e5f1d2a5e0940e3d24b74","tid":796184,"uid":103926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556e82e2e4a4b4a86e87fd69d29e952bb284d845","tid":796184,"uid":124430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1176bbfe5314d830c2363ac4c81c8393f72f1d92","tid":796184,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"利益伸報左先,年頭一路觀望,唔敢亦都無自信入市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最終摸左頂,3萬2入左市,執少少唔肯走,之後跌落三萬忍痛止蝕清晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港股徘徊3萬點果排,各位有印象都記得穿完3萬就即刻升返,曾經有一段上落市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n卒之最後跌落2萬9,我忍唔住又出左手,仲要大手買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後結果大家心裡有數,寫十個慘字都唔夠,恆生指數一直跌,更可怕的係各種大股好似黑色暴雨咁一直落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無錯, 騰訊 ,舜宇, 建設銀行 仲有各種藍籌,呢段期間帳面無左6位數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我明白6位數字對各位黎講只係散紙,但呢D錢,係我靠打工,死慳死抵,一蚊一毫咁儲返黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛市熊市係一個經濟循環,願賭亦都要服輸,本來只打算執少少食餐豪,估唔到嬴粒糖輸間廠<br />\n<br />\n個感覺就係心如止水,諗住繼續自己前途黑暗既人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而,呢段期間,每日上親財經台,圍爐取暖既人當然有<br />\n<br />\n但更加多既係 一班一朝得志既淡友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自問平生無做咩虧心事,玩都只係玩正股,大藍籌<br />\n<br />\n呢班淡友,講既野真係惡毒到不堪入目,恥笑緊同我一樣坐緊貨既苦主都算<br />\n<br />\n有班人仲每日開PO,用自己既燈力,想燈港股繼續向下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢班人, 差唔多每日都要開一個PO,講話聽日會升幾多點,聽日會係大奇跡日,明捧暗踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地呢班苦主,每日睇住呢D PO, 真係心都UP埋 , 終於明白咩叫攞景又贈興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢段時間既財經台,比呢D 一D質素都無既PO 佔晒位,洗晒版<br />\n<br />\n我實在唔明呢D人係咩心態<br />\n<br />\n股市原質上只有望佢升先會有錢賺,有班人唔望升,反望跌,有正股唔玩,係都要玩衍生工具<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句,你地同民國時期,日本侵華既漢奸,有咩分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地既分別就係,漢奸叛國理直氣壯,佢地有自己既理由,原因<br />\n<br />\n當中可能會有落井下石之輩,亦有身在曹營身在漢之人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但呢班仆街死淡友....清一色落井下石...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n落井下石之餘,仲要同班受苦受難既香港人講,加油啊,聽日有人拯救你地啊,你地撐住啊....<br />\n<br />\n我真係R爆頭都諗唔明,點解會有咁多將自己快樂建築係別人痛苦身上既人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望今次港股可以生生性性,一路爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夾死班淡友,夾到佢地灰飛煙滅,往死裡夾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"係咁鍾意高追 咁實抵死㗎"},{"pid":"d3b094162e7fb19fb7ba69973b8b407cf7c1ff50","tid":796184,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T18:52:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d7ffc6e5787d9f17c5bad4bb4814c35ef2a8ed5","tid":796184,"uid":22971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T20:49:23.000Z","msg":"好撚ON9 唔知係咪假膠 皮已負"},{"pid":"9baca80021e79516b1b13a054d3903dd2ed674ce","tid":796184,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"快點夾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}